name: The Creation
description:
"The Creation" - By Bryant W

Divine fiat and fulfillment, the six days of creation; the cosmos created in Genesis and it was so... God saw that it was good.

Enjoy the future!

This artwork was created using old illustrations dating back in the early 1930's that are collaged together and remixed with patterns and other effects in photoshop.

5120px x 5120px .jpg - Date of completion 11/24/2021
